<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UX TTS Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #2b2d31; 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            min-height: 100vh; 
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .login-card {
            background-color: #313338;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-center text-white">
    <div class="login-card">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">UX TTS Dashboard</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-5 text-secondary">Discord Botの設定を<br>ブラウザから快適に管理。</p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-10 mx-auto">
            <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="bi bi-discord me-2"></i>Discordでログイン
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>